|text1     = The total amount of Gold Coins acquired in a match will greatly influence the match's outcome.<br />Remember to keep 50 Gold Coins to accumulate interest, which grants 5 Gold Coins in interest per Node. Every little bit adds up!
|image2    = Tutorial Ascension Tips Economy and Operations 2.png{{subst:void|<!--$UPLOAD:<<SpriteOutput/TutorialPic/TutorialPage_10000801.png>-<Tutorial Ascension Tips Economy and Operations 2.png>-<Tutorial Files>>-->}}
|text2     = Reasonable allocation of Gold Coins:<br />1. Moderate Store refreshing in the early game. Prioritize saving interest and increasing your level to find higher-cost characters in the late game.<br />2. Non-core characters in the lineup do not need to aim for 3 stars, as 2 stars are sufficient, which saves a certain amount of Gold Coins.
